      "author_association": "MEMBER",
      "body": "Persisting the cached balance on disk must be done with care. It could result in situations where the cache is incorrect if the balance calculation operation is interrupted before the updated balances are written to disk. This is particularly important because of imports that effect transactions already in the wallet. An import can make existing inputs and outputs change their IsMine state which will have an effect on the balance.",
